apt-get install iputils-ping

hostname    (give name for you server)
su hostname linux-server   (change name for hostname)
init 6      (restart system)
ping google.com 
wget        (download packages/softwares onto linux system)
curl        (access the application from browser)
netstat -tulpn      (which ports are used in your system)
telnet      (whether particular port is working or not)
telnet localhost 22 
